{"id":"4a46f64bf6a35260c874348ae784faff241bfae79a38871f1b693ff5e8956cfe","text":"用于此 Layer 的 color AOV 名称。此 AOV 必须在 Maya/Katana/Houdini 中设置，否则这个 Canvas DisplayFilter 会退出。"}
{"id":"10aeaae11d28febce45f30f79c629dd858dd8529b9e9f9d488ccb4ccb6fb2f59","text":"以及 Canvas + Hatching："}
{"id":"5566f1273a5a2c87c24f5b59a74c290e1012df173038e59741f65c2f46941147","text":"Canvas Color"}
{"id":"3f2276d19335d9c52cc08819f0a43f8332234108f164dee6b15e39e0cc62ce68","text":"alpha 外部的背景颜色。"}
{"id":"19873e306cc63e02c7e831ee0154baebb632c3b233a8569a6c274965c6b02c9a","text":"Canvas Texture"}
{"id":"ef6fae3537ce3b4da89c17ba5aed0662a3aa14b692a7380986c552f55d367261","text":"为 alpha 外部提供 BG texture；如果留空，则使用 BG Color"}
{"id":"63316a5b5d59554f0855ae89c59948b78c88aa100f7eab2d024e01f6c32cbb3b","text":"Ignore Alpha"}
{"id":"1d33b799fd198d42cf0a45bab91eb259b1e9df0b58054d093379ea44e3d9f934","text":"忽略 alpha，将 BG Color 或 Texture 放到 Canvas 下方的所有内容上。"}
{"id":"d5764c31ff0b6faa4f60837dff874ca6edbb8f0be99cb4ae444c01b68150c254","text":"Compositing Page（合成页面）"}
